<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">話說回來，<delay20 /><tag a="110" b="3" />，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你和剛搬來<tag a="110" b="33" />的新人<delay20 />
打過招呼了嗎？<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />島上的居民慢慢增加，<delay20 />
這裡也會漸漸熱鬧起來吧。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真期待這座島<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />接下來的發展啊，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="007_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天有新面孔<delay20 />來到<delay8 />這座島上了！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然我很想見見對方，<delay20 />但總覺得有點緊張。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你已經和那個人說過話了嗎？<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />剛搬來的第一天，<delay8 />對方應該忙著將行李歸位，<delay20 />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />該什麼時候過去打招呼才好呢？<delay20 />
真是傷腦筋啊，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="007_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="3" />，你聽說了嗎？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />從今天起，這座<tag a="110" b="33" />上<delay20 />
又有新的同伴要搬過來了。<pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那個人剛搬過來，應該會有點不安吧。<delay20 />
所以我打算<delay8 />之後去那個人的家拜訪一下。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你也去跟人家打聲招呼吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="007_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />話說回來，<delay20 />你跟那個人說過話了啊？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />喂喂，<delay20 />你在發什麼呆啊！<pageBreak /><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天島上<delay20 />來了一個新人喔，
你該不會<delay20 />不知道吧？<delay20 />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />現在整座島的人<delay8 />都在討論這個話題！<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也差不多<delay8 />該去拜訪新人的家
和對方打聲招呼了。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你也是，<delay8 />如果願意的話，就去拜訪一趟吧！</message>
	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="011_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />對了，<delay20 />跟你聊到一半讓我想起來了！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我記得<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" />的生日<delay20 />
就是明天吧？<pageBreak /><anim id="Oops" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是的，<delay20 />我竟然會忘了這件事。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />得在今天把<delay8 />禮物給準備好才行，<delay20 />
不過送什麼東西<delay8 />對方才會高興呢？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="011_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哦，<delay20 />話說回來，明天不就是<delay8 />
<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" />的生日嗎！<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我之前已經買好要送禮物了，<delay20 />
希望對方會喜歡。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />畢竟這方面的事我可是完全不懂啊，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="011_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這麼說來，明天就是<delay20 />
<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" />的生日了，<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你準備好<delay8 />禮物了嗎？<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那個人好像不管收到什麼都會高興地收下，<delay20 />
反而讓人<delay8 />不知道該送什麼東西了。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />果然挑禮物才是最困難的啊，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="013" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="013_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天就是<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" /><delay20 />
在這座島上的最後一天了。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然早就知道了，<delay8 />但還是覺得很寂寞啊。<pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />現在搬家的準備好像也已經結束，<delay20 />
沒有其他<delay8 />我能做的事情了，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要不要再去<delay20 />見對方一次呢？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="013_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這一天<delay8 />終於還是來了。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天就是<delay8 /><tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" /><delay20 />
在這座島上的<delay8 />最後一天啦。<pageBreak /><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要是大家一直哭哭啼啼，<delay20 />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />會讓對方擔心<delay8 />而離不開這座島的，<delay20 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這種時候，<delay8 />還是打起精神歡送人家吧！</message>
	<message label="013_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />明天早上<delay8 /><tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" /><delay20 />
就要離開<delay8 />這座島了<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然寂寞，<delay20 />但我也不能一直消沉下去。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />既然我們曾經有緣在同一座島上生活，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那我相信<delay8 />我們一定還會再相遇的，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>